{"type": "article", "id": 29496, "title": "无线入耳式耳机", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-12T23:01:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 64, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160712163923TzREjScq4QxFpv9t.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>来自美国盐湖城的 <a href=\"http://www.firefliesaudio.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">FireFlies Audio</a> 最近推出了一款无线入耳式耳机 Fireflies，它娇小的外型和荧光绿的配色很容易使人联想到夏夜里闪烁着微光的萤火虫。这副耳机由硅胶制成，自适应不同的耳朵大小，哪怕是进行户外极限运动也不会脱落（如果需要双重保障，你也可以使用配套的固定架）。除了免去收纳耳机线的烦恼之外，Fireflies 的充电方式也非常方便，只要装进便携的充电盒即可，续航能力最长可以达到 12 小时。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/876321144/fireflies-affordable-wire-free-earbuds\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 79 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712164036AX5WESaUI61Y9Rv4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.880882\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712164037QVFqTDAoUZOk7Y9M.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712164036Im59tzTkucXqKS2j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160712164036h6WlTLp9iJmq5YdG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}